001package org.jfree.chart.plot;
002
003
004import java.awt.Font;
005import org.jfree.chart.labels.CategoryItemLabelGenerator;
006import org.jfree.chart.internal.Args;
007import java.io.Serializable;
008
009public class SpiderWebPlotProduct3 implements Serializable, Cloneable {
010        private Font labelFont;
011        private CategoryItemLabelGenerator labelGenerator;
012
013        public Font getLabelFont() {
014                return labelFont;
015        }
016
017        public void setLabelFont2(Font labelFont) {
018                this.labelFont = labelFont;
019        }
020
021        public CategoryItemLabelGenerator getLabelGenerator() {
022                return labelGenerator;
023        }
024
025        public void setLabelGenerator2(CategoryItemLabelGenerator labelGenerator) {
026                this.labelGenerator = labelGenerator;
027        }
028
029        /**
030        * Sets the series label font and sends a  {@link PlotChangeEvent}  to all registered listeners.
031        * @param font   the font ( {@code  null}  not permitted).
032        * @see #getLabelFont()
033        */
034        public void setLabelFont(Font font, SpiderWebPlot spiderWebPlot) {
035                Args.nullNotPermitted(font, "font");
036                this.labelFont = font;
037                spiderWebPlot.fireChangeEvent();
038        }
039
040        /**
041        * Sets the label generator and sends a  {@link PlotChangeEvent}  to all registered listeners.
042        * @param generator   the generator ( {@code  null}  not permitted).
043        * @see #getLabelGenerator()
044        */
045        public void setLabelGenerator(CategoryItemLabelGenerator generator) {
046                Args.nullNotPermitted(generator, "generator");
047                this.labelGenerator = generator;
048        }
049
050        public Object clone() throws CloneNotSupportedException {
051                return (SpiderWebPlotProduct3) super.clone();
052        }
053}
